Package: dovetail
Title: Translate Carpentries Lessons
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Joel H.",
      family = "Nitta",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "joelnitta@gmail.com",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4719-7472")
    )
Description: Provides tools to translate a Carpentries-themed lesson from one
  language to another. The resulting translated lesson is an accessible 
  standalone static website. The translation is done using PO files, which
  are meant to be edited by the Carpentries community at large.
